Package com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types

Interface SendClassification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseType, NamedType
    public interface SendClassification
extends NamedType
    Defines interface for all Send classifications that are available that can be used to send an email through the email provider. The send classification has a name and an id for which corresponding setter and getter methods are inherited from NamedType.

      • Methods inherited from interface com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types.BaseType

      • Methods inherited from interface com.day.cq.mcm.emailprovider.types.NamedType

        getName, setName
